Uses of Package
com.tiyb.tev.datamodel

  • Packages that use com.tiyb.tev.datamodel 
    Package Description
    com.tiyb.tev.controller
    This package contains Controllers for the application (both REST and UI).
    com.tiyb.tev.controller.helper
    This package contains helper classes for the controller package.
    com.tiyb.tev.datamodel
    This package contains the Entity classes for working with data in the DB.
    com.tiyb.tev.repository
    Contains Interfaces for working with various database tables.
    com.tiyb.tev.xml
    This package contains classes related to the parsing of XML documents.
  • Classes in com.tiyb.tev.datamodel used by com.tiyb.tev.controller 
    Class Description
    Answer
    Encapsulates the data needed for a Tumblr "Answer" style of post
    Conversation
    Entity representing a conversation, from Tumblr's messaging system
    ConversationMessage
    Entity containing a message from a conversation, from Tumblr's messaging system.
    Hashtag
    Entity for storing hashtags in the DB
    Link
    Encapsulates the data needed for a Tumblr "Link" style of post
    Metadata
    Encapsulates metadata stored in the database for use by the application.
    Photo
    Encapsulates the data needed for a Tumblr "Photo" style of post
    Post
    Encapsulates the data for any Tumblr post.
    Regular
    Encapsulates the data needed for a Tumblr "Regular" style of post (just a normal text post)
    Video
    Encapsulates the data needed for a Tumblr "Video" style of post
  • Classes in com.tiyb.tev.datamodel used by com.tiyb.tev.controller.helper 
    Class Description
    TEVCommonItems
    Common methods/properties to be implemented by all T post types
